events.name: 【152】裏料理会の影 自動実行

parameters: 3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Clea: I apologize for the wait, here is the main dish.

Gourmet Gunil: I'm tired of waiting. If this is your usual
service, it's laughable.

Gourmet Gunil: Oh, an interesting approach, owner. Are you
trying to win me over with this dish?
Gourmet Gunil: Whoa, what are you doing!?

Clea: I apologize, but we don't have the ingredients for
the main dish today, so we are unable to serve it.

Gourmet Gunil: To throw food at a gourmet like me...! I'll
make you compensate with your body, even if I have to force
you!

Clea (If I keep restraining her like this, even though she
doesn't seem accustomed to combat... nggh!?)  Note: The
context suggests that Clea is in a situation where she is
restraining someone and trying to extract information from
them.

Clea (M-My body feels strange... Could it be that if I smell
the pungent fish sauce...!)

Gourmet Gunil: Hehe, that alluring expression... Did you
come here with that intention from the beginning?

Gourmet Gunil: I don't know who's behind this... Well, it
doesn't matter to me anyway.

Gourmet Gunil: Well then, let's enjoy the main dish, shall
we?
Would you like to skip the adult scene?

Gourmet Gunil: I knew you weren't one of the people here.
It's too late for you to realize the critical situation of
this restaurant.

Gourmet Gunil: The front and the back... The culinary
association of the empire is ruled by Lord Baeru.

Gourmet Gunil: Personally, I'm quite taken by your beauty.
I would appreciate it if you could come to my home in
Kanonas next time.

Clea (M-My body still feels shaky... I can't believe the
pungent fish sauce had an aphrodisiac-like effect...)
Clea ...I have to convey the information I obtained.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Owner, Tokyo: Thank you for coming. First, let me inform
you that our situation is very dire.

Owner, Tokyo: Baer specifically asked me to participate in
a cooking showdown as a recommended court chef.

Priestess Sophia: Wouldn't it be advantageous in a cooking
showdown?

Owner, Tokyo: It's not a simple matter. Baer is definitely
engaging in bribery of the judges.

Owner, Tokyo: Baer is a well-known man who is easily swayed
by money. There is no doubt that he is secretly making deals
with Coriba, the gourmet.

Clea: Can we consider this request as a way to prevent
Coriba from participating in the cooking showdown?
Owner, Tokyo: Please take a look at this hand.

Owner, Tokyo: Due to my chronic illness, I can't stop
trembling. I am a person who is finished as a chef.

Mage Relm: The cooking showdown itself won't even happen,
right?
Clea: Is it not possible at the shop?

Owner, Tokyo: A cooking showdown to recommend a court
chef... There are still no disciples who can withstand that
pressure.

Owner, Tokyo: I want you to bring a chef who has the
courage and passion that I can support!

Thief Nora: Let's ask Chef Meri! My mom said she's an
amazing cook too!

Owner, Tokyo: I will procure ingredients and such. Once the
preparations are complete, let's meet up in the desert city
of Ammos.
Clea: Understood, let's meet in Ammos.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
